---
---

<section class="substack" id="substack" aria-labelledby="substack-title">
  <div class="substack__bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <img
      src="/images/product-recover.jpg"
      alt=""
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
      width="1600"
      height="1000"
    />
    <div class="substack__bg-veil"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="substack__inner">
      <div class="substack__col">
        <p class="eyebrow reveal">Content ecosystem</p>
        <h2 id="substack-title" class="substack__title split">
          {'Want the science?'.split(' ').map((w) => (<span class="split__word"><span>{w}</span></span>))}
          <br />
          <em>{'Read our Substack.'.split(' ').map((w) => (<span class="split__word"><span>{w}</span></span>))}</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="substack__copy reveal" data-stagger="2">
          The science layer of XYVON lives on Substack: evidence reviews,
          ingredient dives, and the thinking behind every dose. Written by
          Peter. Not paywalled. Never marketing in disguise.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="substack__col substack__col--right">
        <form class="substack__form reveal" data-stagger="3" action="#" method="post" aria-label="Subscribe to XYVON Substack">
          <label class="caps--wide" for="email">Subscribe</label>
          <div class="substack__field">
            <input id="email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required autocomplete="email" />
            <button type="submit" class="substack__submit" aria-label="Subscribe">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M2 9h14M10 3l6 6-6 6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
              </svg>
            </button>
          </div>
          <p class="substack__legal">
            One clear CTA. No pop-ups. No countdown timers. Unsubscribe in one click.
          </p>
        </form>

        <ul class="substack__list reveal" data-stagger="4">
          <li>
            <span class="caps--wide">Issue 04</span>
            <h3>Why we rejected magnesium oxide on day one</h3>
            <p>Bioavailability math, not a marketing decision.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="caps--wide">Issue 03</span>
            <h3>Cycle-aware electrolytes: what the literature actually says</h3>
            <p>A literature review without the wellness translation layer.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="caps--wide">Issue 02</span>
            <h3>The “every ingredient earns its place” test</h3>
            <p>How we killed three ingredients that would have made shelf-sense.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .substack {
    position: relative;
    isolation: isolate;
    background: var(--xyv-black-deep);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--xyv-line);
  }

  .substack__bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .substack__bg img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    filter: grayscale(1) contrast(1.1);
    opacity: 0.18;
  }

  .substack__bg-veil {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--xyv-black-deep) 0%, rgba(11, 11, 12, 0.85) 50%, var(--xyv-black-deep) 100%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at right, rgba(184, 115, 51, 0.12), transparent 55%);
  }

  .substack__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-9);
    align-items: start;
    position: relative;
  }

  .substack__col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--sp-5); }

  .substack__title {
    font-size: var(--fs-display);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .substack__title em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--xyv-copper);
  }

  .substack__copy {
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-size: var(--fs-lead);
    max-width: 50ch;
  }

  /* ---------- Form ---------- */
  .substack__form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-3);
    padding: var(--sp-6);
    border: 1px solid var(--xyv-line);
    border-radius: var(--r-lg);
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(184, 115, 51, 0.1), transparent 60%),
      var(--xyv-black-soft);
  }

  .substack__form label { color: var(--xyv-copper); }

  .substack__field {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--xyv-line-strong);
    border-radius: var(--r-pill);
    padding: 0.3em 0.35em 0.3em 1.25em;
    transition: border-color var(--dur-med) var(--ease-smooth);
  }

  .substack__field:focus-within { border-color: var(--xyv-copper); }

  .substack__field input {
    flex: 1;
    background: transparent;
    border: 0;
    color: var(--xyv-off-white);
    font: inherit;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    padding: 0.8em 0;
    outline: none;
  }

  .substack__field input::placeholder { color: var(--ink-faint); }

  .substack__submit {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--xyv-copper);
    color: var(--xyv-black-deep);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: background var(--dur-med) var(--ease-smooth), transform var(--dur-med) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .substack__submit:hover {
    background: var(--xyv-off-white);
    transform: rotate(-10deg) scale(1.05);
  }

  .substack__legal {
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin-top: var(--sp-1);
  }

  /* ---------- List ---------- */
  .substack__list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-top: var(--sp-6);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-5);
  }

  .substack__list li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 72px minmax(0, 1fr);
    grid-template-areas:
      'meta title'
      '.    desc';
    column-gap: var(--sp-5);
    row-gap: var(--sp-2);
    padding-bottom: var(--sp-5);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--xyv-line);
  }

  .substack__list li:last-child { border-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; }

  .substack__list .caps--wide {
    grid-area: meta;
    color: var(--xyv-copper);
    padding-top: 3px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    align-self: start;
  }

  .substack__list h3 {
    grid-area: title;
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .substack__list p {
    grid-area: desc;
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    min-width: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .substack__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .substack__col { align-items: center; text-align: center; }
    .substack__title { margin-inline: auto; }
    .substack__copy { margin-inline: auto; }

    .substack__form { width: 100%; }
    .substack__form label { text-align: center; }
    .substack__legal { text-align: center; }

    .substack__list { width: 100%; }
    .substack__list li {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      grid-template-areas:
        'meta'
        'title'
        'desc';
      row-gap: var(--sp-2);
      text-align: center;
      justify-items: center;
    }
    .substack__list h3 { text-align: center; }
    .substack__list p { text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
